<P class=MsoBodyTextCxSpFirst 
style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 36pt; mso-mirror-indents: yes; mso-char-indent-count: 3.0"><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 黑体">第十一条<SPAN 
lang=EN-US><SPAN style="mso-tab-count: 1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 
</SPAN></SPAN></SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt">满足下列条件之一的<SPAN 
style="LETTER-SPACING: -4.45pt">，</SPAN>属于在某一时段内履行履约义<SPAN 
style="LETTER-SPACING: -0.05pt">务</SPAN>；否则，属于在某一时点履行履约义务：</SPAN><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoBodyTextCxSpMiddle 
style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 36pt; mso-mirror-indents: yes; mso-char-indent-count: 3.0"><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt">（一）客户在企业履约的同时即取得并消耗企业履约所带来的经济利益。</SPAN><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoBodyTextCxSpMiddle 
style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 36pt; mso-mirror-indents: yes; mso-char-indent-count: 3.0"><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt">（二）客户能够控制企业履约过程中在建的商品。</SPAN><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoBodyTextCxSpMiddle 
style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 36pt; mso-mirror-indents: yes; mso-char-indent-count: 3.0"><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt">（三）企业履约过程中所产出的商品具有不可替代用途，且该企业在整个合同期间内有权就累计至今已完成的履约部分收取款项。</SPAN><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoBodyTextCxSpMiddle 
style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 36pt; mso-mirror-indents: yes; mso-char-indent-count: 3.0"><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt">具有不可替代用途，是指因合同限制或实际可行性限制，企业不能轻易地将商品用于其他用途。</SPAN><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoBodyTextCxSpMiddle 
style="LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 36pt; mso-mirror-indents: yes; mso-char-indent-count: 3.0"><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt">有权就累计至今已完成的履约部分收取款项，是指在由于客户或其他方原因终止合同的情况下，企业有权就累计至今已完成的履约部分收取能够补偿其已发生成本和合理利润的款项，并且该权利具有法律约束力。</SPAN><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoBodyTextCxSpMiddle 
style="MARGIN: 2.9pt 5.65pt 6pt 0cm; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 29.95pt; mso-mirror-indents: yes; mso-add-space: auto"><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 黑体">第十二条 
</SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt">对于在某一时段内履行的履约义务，企业应当在</SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt"><FONT 
face=宋体> </FONT></SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt">该段时间内按照履约进度确认收入，但是，履约进度不能合理确</SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt"><FONT 
face=宋体> </FONT></SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt">定的除外。企业应当考虑商品的性质，采用产出法或投入法确定</SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt"><FONT 
face=宋体> </FONT></SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt">恰当的履约进度。其中，产出法是根据已转移给客户的商品对于</SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt"><FONT 
face=宋体> </FONT></SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt">客户的价值确定履约进度；投入法是根据企业为履行履约义务的</SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt"><FONT 
face=宋体> </FONT></SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt">投入确定履约进度。对于类似情况下的类似履约义务，企业应当采用相同的方法确定履约进度。</SPAN><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoBodyTextCxSpMiddle 
style="MARGIN: 2.95pt 5.65pt 6pt 0cm; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 29.95pt; mso-mirror-indents: yes; mso-add-space: auto"><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt">当履约进度不能合理确定时，企业已经发生的成本预计能够</SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt"><FONT 
face=宋体> </FONT></SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt">得到补偿的，应当按照已经发生的成本金额确认收入，直到履约</SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt">进度能够合理确定为止。</SPAN><SPAN 
lang=EN-US 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt"><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P class=MsoBodyTextCxSpMiddle 
style="MARGIN: 2.95pt 5.65pt 6pt 0cm; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; TEXT-INDENT: 29.95pt; mso-mirror-indents: yes; mso-add-space: auto"><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 黑体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 黑体">第十三条 
</SPAN><SPAN 
style="FONT-SIZE: 12pt; FONT-FAMILY: 宋体; LINE-HEIGHT: 150%; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-fareast; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt">对于在某一时点履行的履约义务，企业应当在客户取得相关商品控制权时点确认收入。在判断客户是否已取得商</SPAN><SPAN 
